extendedInfo.description: Join Pastors Mark and Sumiko Stroud as they teach the Bible in an easy to understand format that is humorous, inspiring, and educational. New sermons are added regularly that are sure to bless your soul. You can have a daily devotional or Bible study while listening to the mp3 audio or watching one of our youtube videos. Our goal is to reach the lost for Christ, empower the believer, and add joy to your day. Your life will be forever changed by the "Good News" of Jesus Christ!Visit our website at www.kingdomrock.org for our complete archive of sermons. Please share this free app with a friend and help us spread the gospel around the world.
